      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved to showroom standards, it exhibits no signs of wear, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every component functions with absolute precision, ensuring a driving experience that mirrors its original factory delivery. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of peerless integrity and aesthetic perfection.",
