    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty in person! I have babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly pristine shape\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and the interior is still flawless. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but I\u2019m ready to pass it on to someone who will love it just as much as I have. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message and let\u2019s get you a test drive!",
      "price": 46500.0,
